{"type":"message","id":"9e159328","parentId":"3f0f861d","timestamp":"2026-02-28T14:42:40.535Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"任务已经被删除了。让我直接用 `--message` 参数创建一个新任务，让它在 main session 中执行 shell 命令。\n\n实际上，从之前的 cron 任务列表来看，`novel-review-and-revise` 任务的 `session` 是 `isolated`，这意味着它应该在独立的 session 中运行，而不是在 main session 中。\n\n让我检查一下如何创建一个运行 shell 命令的 cron 任务。从 OpenClaw 文档来看，cron 任务有两种类型：\n1. Agent 任务：发送消息给 agent\n2. Shell 任务：执行 shell 命令\n\n看起来 `--command` 参数可能是用于 agent 任务的。让我尝试用 `--system-event` 或 `--message` 参数。\n\n实际上，让我直接用 `openclaw cron edit` 来修改现有任务。等等，任务已经被删除了。\n\n让我尝试创建一个 agent 任务，让它执行 shell 命令。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e417b51a64c145a685357441","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add \\\n  --name \"novel-review-and-revise-v3\" \\\n  --cron \"0 6 * * *\" \\\n  --message \"执行小说审查修改任务: node /root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/novel-review-and-revise-v3.js\" \\\n  --session isolated \\\n  --no-deliver \\\n  --exact 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_21a140ff07dc4a13b2bb464a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron list 2>&1 | grep \"novel\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":200,"output":305,"cacheRead":59712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60217,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772289746168}}
